time supporter of astronaut safety, and indeed, it has been my pri-
mary goal in relation to the U.S. space program. And I have argued
for  years  that  we  need  to  do  everything  we  can  to  insure  that  the
men  and  women  who  are  launched  into  outer  space  are  prepared
