investigations aimed at addressing the problems that led to the ac-
cident,  and  these  investigations  culminated  with  the  CAIB  report
that  outlined  suggestions  for  NASA.  So  I  know  that  Administrator
Griffin  and  his  team  have  taken  these  suggestions  seriously  and
have implemented a series of changes at NASA to address the con-
cerns.

