24

Mark Bauer, specialist in psychiatry, Professor of Psychiatry, Brown University
and Providence Veterans Affairs Medical Center.
James Fraser, Captain U.S. Navy retired, specialist in aerospace medicine, cur-
rently Deputy Federal Air Surgeon, Federal Aviation Administration.
Sandra  Yerkes,  Captain  U.S.  Navy  retired,  specialist  in  psychiatry,  currently
