IMPLEMENTATION OF RECOMMENDATIONS

Dr. GRIFFIN. Well, I don’t know by what date Dr. Williams plans
to  bring  recommendations  or  an  assessment  back  to  Shana  and  I.
He  probably  does.  My  own  view  is  that  this  is  both  important  and
urgent,  but  it  is  more  important  to  get  right  than  to  get  done

